In the year 2077, the world is dominated by artificial intelligence, humans can no longer contain and control the monster they have made.

10 years ago, the AI massacred 90% of humans on the planet, the lucky ones were able to make it to the hidden bunkers underground, these bunkers were built to hide humanity from the oncoming threat...

Over the past 10 years, AIs have continued hunting for the remaining humans. Right now your radar has detected a rouge AI that is coming for you.
You need to gather and assemble the pieces of your gun as well as some bullets if you're going to survive an AI attack...
You have 45 seconds before it's too late, hurry up!

Hold Space Bar to Skip
Press Space Bar to Continue
Although you successfully defeat the AI, you are already exposed to other AI all around the world, they are coming for you. The doomsday of humans is coming...
